            <div id=3D"editor" contenteditable=3D"true" tabindex=3D"0"><p s=
tyle=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">
DSL2XDXF</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in"><br>

</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">Only in Russian,
sorry.</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in"><br>

</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">Converter of Lingvo
8 DSL dictionary source files into XML language in XDXF format.
Supports both Unicode DSL and ANSI DSL. Compatible with DSL files
from earlier Lingvo versions.</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in"><br>

</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">Command format:</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in"><br>

</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">dslx2dxf.py
=E2=80=93[T|X|E|S|A] [-h] [-n &lt;name&gt;] [-z &lt;full_name&gt;] [-d
&lt;descr&gt;] [-f &lt;from&gt;] [-t &lt;to&gt;] [-a &lt;file&gt;]
[-i] &lt;DSL_name&gt; [&lt;target_directory&gt;]</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in"><br>

</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">Parameters enclosed
in square brackets are optional.</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in"><br>

</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">Options:</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">- -h =E2=80=94 Help.</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">- -T =E2=80=94 Dictionar=
y
type: "translation"</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">- -X =E2=80=94 Dictionar=
y
type: "explanatory"</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">- -E =E2=80=94 Dictionar=
y
type: "encyclopedia"</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">- -S =E2=80=94 Dictionar=
y
type: "spelling"</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">- -A =E2=80=94 Dictionar=
y
type: "audio"</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in"><br>

</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">More than one
dictionary type parameter may be specified, but at least one is
required.</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in"><br>

</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">Metadata options:</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">- -n &lt;name&gt; =E2=80=
=94
Short dictionary name. If not specified, taken from the DSL file.</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">- -z &lt;full_name&gt;
=E2=80=94 Full dictionary name.</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">- -d &lt;descr&gt; =E2=
=80=94
Dictionary description.</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">- -f &lt;from&gt; =E2=80=
=94
Source language.</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">- -t &lt;to&gt; =E2=80=
=94
Target language.</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">- -a &lt;file&gt; =E2=80=
=94
Path to abbreviations file.</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">- -i =E2=80=94 Pretty
formatting.</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in"><br>

</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">Example:</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">python dsl2xdxf.py
-EX -n "AppliedMathematics (Ru-En)" -d "My dictionary"
-f Russian -t English /var/dict/dict.dsl</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in"><br>

</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">The dictionary will
be saved as:</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">/var/dict/appliedmathema=
tics
(ru-en)/appliedmathematics (ru-en).xdxf</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in"><br>

</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">Additional behavior:</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">- .ann annotation
files are appended into &lt;description&gt;.</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">- abbrev.dsl /
abrv.dsl files may be imported.</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">- matching .bmp
files are copied.</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">- referenced
multimedia files are copied.</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">- output names are
lowercased.</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in"><br>

</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">DSL Tag Conversion
Table:</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in"><br>

</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">[b][/b] -&gt;
&lt;b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">[i][/i] -&gt;
&lt;i&gt;&lt;/i&gt;</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">[u][/u] -&gt;
&lt;u&gt;&lt;/u&gt;</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">[c][/c] -&gt;
&lt;color&gt;&lt;/color&gt;</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">[trn][/trn] -&gt;
&lt;dtrn&gt;&lt;/dtrn&gt;</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">[ex][/ex] -&gt;
&lt;example&gt;&lt;/example&gt;</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">[com][/com] -&gt;
&lt;comment&gt;&lt;/comment&gt;</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">[s]file[/s] -&gt;
&lt;rref&gt;file&lt;/rref&gt;</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">[url]link[/url] -&gt;
&lt;iref&gt;link&lt;/iref&gt;</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">[ref]link[/ref] -&gt;
&lt;kref&gt;&lt;/kref&gt;</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">[sub][/sub] -&gt;
&lt;sub&gt;&lt;/sub&gt;</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">[sup][/sup] -&gt;
&lt;sup&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">[t][/t] -&gt;
&lt;transcription&gt;&lt;/transcription&gt;</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in"><br>

</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">Nested article
syntax:</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in"><br>

</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">@ heading</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">body</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in"><br>

</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">becomes:</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in"><br>

</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">&lt;subarticle&gt;</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in"> &lt;key&gt;heading&lt;/=
key&gt;</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in"> &lt;def&gt;body&lt;/def=
&gt;</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">&lt;/subarticle&gt;</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in"><br>

</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">Special
substitutions:</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">~      -&gt; current
headword</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">^~     -&gt; current
headword with changed first-letter case</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">(...)  -&gt;
optional part</p>
<p style=3D"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0in">{...}  -&gt;
non-sortable part</p></div>
       =20
       =20
       =20
        </body></html>
